{"tid":1853331,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"沈旭暉 : 屌柒連登仔 再任由藍絲攻擊醫護 香港死撚緊","createTime":"2020-01-31T02:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T13:40:37.000Z","uid":21470,"like":47,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f21b9a1bb552ebec51096490729ce7f7d631a41b","tid":1853331,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"堅離地城：沈旭暉國際生活台 Simon's Glos World<br />\n<br />\n昨天說過，林鄭月娥堅持不封關的劇本，就是運用「群眾鬥群眾」的伎倆，「引蛇出洞」，逼不勝負荷的醫護人員採取行動，然後批鬥「黑醫」自私自利。雖然早有準備，但林鄭打手的下流程度，依然令人意外，這次「頭號警察KOL」光頭劉Sir和屈小姐世紀雙劍合璧，批鬥香港醫護人員是「逃兵」、「魔鬼」、「希望他們感染新型冠狀病毒」、「要處決」，文革作風，令人歎為觀止。<br />\n<br />\n昨天四百多位瑪麗醫院等醫生護士教授實名聯署，包括好些行內德高望重的重量級權威，恐怕難免成為下一步目標。而劉Sir身為香港特區政府公務員，居然牽頭批鬥香港醫護人員，明顯違反公務員守則，要是縱容，日後林鄭政府只會更無法無天。假如林鄭這幾天還拒絕全面封關，未來的批鬥，醫護人員受的壓力，只會更瘋狂。<br />\n<br />\n這早已不是香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/photos/a.224514904249334/3012215188812611/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%2Fphotos%2Fa.224514904249334%2F3012215188812611%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=784225e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/photos/a.224514904249334/3012215188812611/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"1a79735a043690ef2feb75930792ff0442709e39","tid":1853331,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"我大佬"},{"pid":"abd0bf9dec94688a9f86fb0f2b649ce6dc182ca0","tid":1853331,"uid":276548,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:19:17.000Z","msg":"咁鐘意屌支持全體罷工<br />\n反正死都係死班老野廢老藍絲先"},{"pid":"949aa8328a3ba7410e93d672600b98da12e33bf4","tid":1853331,"uid":162272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:24:47.000Z","msg":"係罷工就快手啦 再唔係全體辭職 洗怕佢批鬥"},{"pid":"da2ca4c97e9171055cbe25f7a0ecaec3cfaa92c7","tid":1853331,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工<br />\n<br />\n封關係必然<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解唔做"},{"pid":"29b0de5961527b4a496c58562eeab8341c15a8e3","tid":1853331,"uid":36065,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"1月29 又話罷 而家就話2月3 <br />\n<br />\n喂 人地摸撚穿左你個底啦"},{"pid":"3e2217403bff7a089d735b117a1e3a788c248c1f","tid":1853331,"uid":38775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:31:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n親政府班人真係當醫護係軍人/紀律部隊<br />\n隻光頭狗, 屈賤婦又係呢種論調<br />\n將軍澳醫院行政總監個論調都係人終需一死, 為光榮而戰都係對軍人先會咁講"},{"pid":"a26dce6871089a3010a8770c3db54880e3794148","tid":1853331,"uid":38775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18893a81fa93a9544bf2de7261de4cc185f6062a","tid":1853331,"uid":38775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3d6c82e4c1a310fc3ab91af050bbbbcc5369604","tid":1853331,"uid":128369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f4631f1e22394012d7e81740b61ce9d4b8aad7","tid":1853331,"uid":201237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"一定要支持醫護罷工"},{"pid":"6c70d1e3fc2c0644abbbaa5132a589f145e9fad5","tid":1853331,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:02:42.000Z","msg":"抱歉借個位，啱用求幫p牌輕輕推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【有圖】希望唔係17k黃絲比人誤導買口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854451</a>"},{"pid":"c0324a4fb8267c6d4eb5c9b041e134a0d22495e8","tid":1853331,"uid":92038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:18:41.000Z","msg":"想問啲醫護罷工文宣連登多d定fb多d<br />\n本身草左一疊fb揾返嚟嘅文宣<br />\n但太耐無上連登唔覺有<br />\n無大型衝擊參加想轉做文宣師"},{"pid":"7c7309463153da43ca35bcee9c36648269cd70b1","tid":1853331,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score